title: Iron Man TAS DVDrip season 1,2,crossovers cartoon animated
description:
This is the complete Iron Man animated series, including cross-over episodes on the Incredible Hulk and Spider Man cartoons.

Quality: Average quality PAL DVDrips or PAL TVrips from a station without logos. Cross-over episodes are TVrips with logos. Season 2 episodes are better quality than Season 1.

Source: Several other torrents, and eMule.

-- Note: I have re-timed all episodes of the 2nd season of Iron Man from PAL 25fps to the original 23.976fps, so that the kick-arse screamin' guitar rock soundtrack doesn't sound like garbage. (1st season soundtrack is lame either way, so I didn't bother with those.) I also re-timed the cross-over episodes so Spidey and Hulk's soundtracks are true.)

Also contains version 3.1 of the Cartoon Rating Guide for Smart Adults.
